Package: cocons
Type: Package
Title: Covariate-Based Covariance Functions for Nonstationary Spatial Modeling
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Federico Blasi [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9337-7154>), Reinhard Furrer [ctb] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6319-2332>)
